<?xml version="1.0"?>
<uiml>
    <interface>
        <structure>		
			<part class="Frame" id="Frame">
			
			<part class="Entry" id="EValue"/>
			<part class="Label" id="LValue"/>
			
			<part class="Label" id="LFrom"/>
			<part class="Combo" id="CFrom"/>			
			
			<part class="Label" id="LTo"/>
			<part class="Combo" id="CTo"/>		
			
			<part class="Entry" id="EResult"/>
			<part class="Label" id="LResult"/>
			
			<part class="Button" id="BConvert"/>
			
			</part>
	
		
        </structure>
        <style>
			<property part-name="Frame" name="position">5,5</property>
			<property part-name="Frame" name="size">400,275</property>
			
			<property part-name="EValue" name="position">150,15</property>	
			<property part-name="EValue" name="size">120,25</property>	
			<property part-name="LValue" name="position">50,15</property>	
			<property part-name="LValue" name="text">Value:</property>
			
			<property part-name="LFrom" name="position">50,72</property>
			<property part-name="LFrom" name="text">From:</property>
			<property part-name="CFrom" name="position">150, 72</property>
			<property part-name="CFrom" name="content">
		  		<constant model="list">
					<constant value="U.S. dollar"/>
					<constant value="Euro"/>
					<constant value="British pound"/>					
				</constant>
			</property>
			<property part-name="CFrom" name="selectedIndex">0</property>			
			
			<property part-name="LTo" name="position">50,129</property>	
			<property part-name="LTo" name="text">To:</property>
			<property part-name="LTo" name="position">50,129</property>
			<property part-name="LTo" name="text">From:</property>
			<property part-name="CTo" name="position">150, 129</property>
			<property part-name="CTo" name="content">
		  		<constant model="list">
					<constant value="U.S. dollar"/>
					<constant value="Euro"/>
					<constant value="British pound"/>					
				</constant>
			</property>
			<property part-name="CTo" name="selectedIndex">1</property>
				
			<property part-name="EResult" name="position">150,185</property>
			<property part-name="EResult" name="size">120,25</property>	
			<property part-name="EResult" name="readonly">true</property>
			<property part-name="LResult" name="position">50,185</property>	
			<property part-name="LResult" name="text">Result:</property>
			
			<property part-name="BConvert" name="position">75,225</property>
			<property part-name="BConvert" name="size">175,25</property>
			<property part-name="BConvert" name="label">Convert</property>

			
        </style>
        <behavior>
			<rule>
				<condition>
					<event part-name="BConvert" class="ButtonPressed"/>
				</condition>
				<action>
				<property part-name="EResult" name="text">
					<call name="CurrencyConverter.Convert">
						<param name="amount">
							<property part-name="EValue" name="text"/>
						</param>
						<param name="from">
							<property part-name="CTo" name="entry"/>
						</param>
						<param name="to">
							<property part-name="CFrom" name="entry"/>
						</param>
					</call>					
				</property>
				</action>
			</rule>
        </behavior>
    </interface>
	<peers>
		<presentation base="swf-1.1.uiml"/>
        <logic id="converter">
            <d-component id="CurrencyConverter" maps-to="CurrencyConverter">
                <d-method id="Convert" return-type="System.Double" maps-to="Convert">
                    <d-param id="amount" type="System.Double"/>
                    <d-param id="from" type="System.String"/>
                    <d-param id="to" type="System.String"/>
                </d-method>
            </d-component>
        </logic>
	</peers>
</uiml>
